Call,Loop,provides,web,based,voice,broadcasting,SMS,messaging,and,appointment,reminder,software,Call,Loop,enables,users,to,send,voice,and,text,messages,to,large,audiences,and,offers,an,API,allowing,developers,to,integrate,Call,Loop,s,SMS,and,voice,capabilities,into,their,applications,The,API,allows,applications,to,add,or,remove,contacts,from,groups,and,to,send,SMS,texts,or,voice,broadcasts,Potential,uses,include,automated,notifications,customer,service,order,status,updates,and,more